node.text: Omggg this is so dope, thank you so much @courtneyakemp for giving me this opportunity! You’re such an inspiration and an amazing person! 3 years ago I would’ve never thought I’d have a role on one of the biggest shows out today! Even down to the message and point behind the character I play is amazing because that’s real life! Never acted on a serious note a day in my life, and here you come turning a dream into reality 😢Sometimes it still feels surreal but thank you thank you thank you for believing in me 🥺❤️ Tune in @ MIDNIGHT , ALL NEW EPISODE PowerBook ll: Ghost 👻  Download the @starz app ✨
